}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-300","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2","children":"1. Data We Do Not Collect"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-8 leading-relaxed","children":["- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Plaintext Files:"}]," We never receive unencrypted files.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Private Keys / Seed phrases:"}]," We never request or store your wallet master secrets.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"IP Addresses:"}]," We aggressively strip IP-logging from our Node.js load balancers.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Unencrypted Metadata:"}]," Folder names and asset classifications are salted and hashed."]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2","children":"2. Data We *Must* Process"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-8 leading-relaxed","children":["To provide the core functionality of the Dead-Man Protocol, the following data is processed by our infrastructure:",["$","br",null,{}],["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Public Wallet Addresses:"}]," Stored on our MongoDB cluster to identify users and authenticate API requests utilizing EIP-4361 standard signatures.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Heartbeat Timestamps:"}]," To compute inactivity thresholds for the automated release smart contract.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Encrypted Blobs:"}]," AES-256-GCM cipher-text, temporarily held prior to IPFS pinning.",["$","br",null,{}],"- ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Email Addresses (Optional):"}]," If you choose to enable Web2 alerting, your email is stored alongside your public key."]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2","children":"3. Third Party & On-Chain Sharing"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-8 leading-relaxed","children":["Due to the nature of decentalized smart contracts, any `Nominee Public Key` or `Execution Logic` you broadcast to the Polygon blockchain becomes immutable, transparent public data. While the ",["$","em",null,{"children":"payload content"}]," remains heavily encrypted, the transparent metadata showing that Wallet A has designated Wallet B as a successor is visible on block explorers.",["$","br",null,{}],["$","br",null,{}],"We use Web3.Storage for decentralized pinning. They follow strict cryptographic constraints, but you must acknowledge that CIDs pinned to IPFS are distributed globally."]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 border-b border-slate-800 pb-2","children":"4. Law Enforcement Subpoenas"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mb-8 leading-relaxed","children":["If legally compelled by a recognized international jurisdiction, we will comply. ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"However"}],", compliance solely means handing over encrypted blobs and the zero-knowledge metadata we possess. We do not have backdoors. We cannot forge Shamir Shares. ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"We mathematically cannot decrypt your data for the government, or anyone else."}]]}]]}]]}]}],null],null],null]},[null,["$","$L2",null,{"parallelRouterKey":"children","segmentPath":["children","privacy","children"],"error":"$undefined","errorStyles":"$undefined","errorScripts":"$undefined","template":["$","$L3",null,{}],"templateStyles":"$undefined","templateScripts":"$undefined","notFound":"$undefined","notFoundStyles":"$undefined"}]],null]},[[[["$","link","0",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/css/7cca8e2c5137bd71.css","precedence":"next","crossOrigin":"$undefined"}],["$","link","1",{"rel":"stylesheet","href":"/_next/static/css/7e86088dd9326bd1.css","precedence":"next","crossOrigin":"$undefined"}]],["$","html",null,{"lang":"en","className":"dark","suppressHydrationWarning":true,"children":["$","bo